{"tid":1911823,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單啲講，熱狗就係有以下特性","createTime":"2020-03-05T15:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T00:58:15.000Z","uid":27553,"like":143,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"f526d5311fc501116b0f9853cca725fd89eb8c85","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"經過半年觀察，呢班人有好多明確既特點(如有更多歡迎補充)：<br />\n<br />\n對泛民主派有極強烈嘅仇恨，認為泛民既邪惡程度不亞於港共。如果有得揀佢地寧願泛民滅黨先於共產黨滅黨。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但從來冇提及邊個政黨既信念先係最合佢地意。</span></strong><br />\n另外，佢地對獨派亦有同樣仇恨，對所有港獨都以偽獨派稱呼。<br />\n<br />\n對所有黃絲發起嘅運動極度反感，黃色經濟圈等於鳩做，唱榮光係打飛機，日程表等於送頭，總之你做乜都係錯。以嘲笑同路人為樂。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但從來冇提及應該點樣抗爭先係正確</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n非常崇拜美國，認為只有美國先係香港既救世主。經常發起大量白宮聯署，認為簽名比上述抗爭有效，並表示拯救香港既唯一方法就係等待美國制裁。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但從來冇提及美國要老奉幫你既原因</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n選舉方面，經常提倡射落海唔益任何派系，認為贏出所有制度下選舉皆是endorse政權。19年區議會如是，黎緊既功能組別爭議亦如是。最好就係建制派全取70席。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但從來冇提及有效既議會外抗爭方法</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n疑似熱狗/陳云根信徒。之所以用&ldquo;疑似&rdquo;係因為佢地唔認自己係熱狗，但經常share鄭松泰、熱血時報、陳云根文章。<br />\n<br />\n以示公允，呢班人都係唔好叫佢地做熱狗，咁應該點稱呼佢地好？同埋呢班人既心路歷程究竟係點黎？<br />\n話呢班人係敵人又唔似，話佢係自己人又唔係。對抗呢個政府已經好攰，唔想再嘥時間應付呢啲派系爭拗<br />\n<br />\n返過工既都知一直ban橋又唔俾橋既同事係最乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有巴絲係上述所講既人，不如你係下面講下其實你地想點？<br />\n<br />\n真係講得好撚中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原post：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1908384/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1908384/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4d5d230df480e3727684b5ba933290482f0087eb","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"仲有fb入面大量熱狗衛星page不斷spin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99424018fe121da07e0062ce6b14316042d02a97","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79c4a7f6c7da95e22789dbb1100ec8ce0a33148","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a2e91458f7a2b9a1b66f879410a1b12107a9e6","tid":1911823,"uid":236414,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"五隻字就係反對反對派，監察飯民用<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"c940b564b3bddb958c7c0b3bed5e2e612d57273c","tid":1911823,"uid":227801,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前都冇咩特別太反感，2016年仲投左鄭松泰<br />\n低自從舊年反送中開始，真係項唔撚順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有野都反對，6.9遊行(差唔多所有遊行)反對、區譏會選舉冇用/反對、黃色經濟圈反對etc..........................................."},{"pid":"2a3d7168d5cb5bc9a8223e6832d23e81486b33c0","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"75a2e91458f7a2b9a1b66f879410a1b12107a9e6","tid":1911823,"uid":236414,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"五隻字就係反對反對派，監察飯民用<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"熱狗屌自己人仲落力過建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fe255e1b01b0c037371d5a5b18169e675229fe","tid":1911823,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\