st都無人駁到樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4417ac581aa5aa769ea8e5a73d81cba8c009fd0e","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"121610ddc308ee5f80e2584804735ba97ff99ec9","tid":1911823,"uid":141097,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2a3d7168d5cb5bc9a8223e6832d23e81486b33c0","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"75a2e91458f7a2b9a1b66f879410a1b12107a9e6","tid":1911823,"uid":236414,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"五隻字就係反對反對派，監察飯民用<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"熱狗屌自己人仲落力過建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:21:03.000Z","msg":"屌敵人嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:24:08.000Z","msg":"不斷笑鳩同路人最有用<br />\n一副眾人皆醉唯我獨醒既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820b8d1671885853d088180a58aede35ae362e37","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f964b5f1c57f844d16f48ce8c752cac49a11b3a","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:28:20.000Z","msg":"仲有條陳雲<br />\n岩聽就話有食藥<br />\n明搞分化就未食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a05747913e0dd0a31b20c8fd027959563b2196b","tid":1911823,"uid":303854,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:28:21.000Z","msg":"真心想知佢地想點<br />\n你ban都唔緊要 但又唔肯講應該點做<br />\n最煩就係日日係度發晦氣咁話人地做嘅野無用 由得香港死算啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排個個叫人登記做選民 佢地又第一個衝出黎發晦氣笑人：投哂泛民就啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等食屎啦<br />\n但又唔講如果唔理立法會 可以點阻止建制話哂事<img src=\