 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柏洋(熱狗仔) 俾黑警告就揾當值律師，自己同蝗后就拎錢去加拿大食好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca09563bb7e1d21cce60b406f258b2569d8da25b","tid":1911823,"uid":257190,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"75a2e91458f7a2b9a1b66f879410a1b12107a9e6","tid":1911823,"uid":236414,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"五隻字就係反對反對派，監察飯民用<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:47:06.000Z","msg":"佢地一副眾人階醉嘅態度好難頂<br />\n仲有7左唔認，然後笑鳩你唔夠IQ，好L 7<br />\n但佢地有時有d point啱聽，就聽下<br />\n自己係睇唔到自己人有咩不足，其他人尤其佢地咁憎泛民就一定睇到<br />\n過去咁多個月，大家都知道泛民係要監察<br />\n我亦都好開心，大家係網上監察完泛民佢聽會聽<br />\n<br />\n6 7 8 9 10 月大家都可以冇bias咁學習，AI咁進步，希望而家大家都可以<br />\n冇大台敵人就打唔到你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84738be76037e746a7621a61e786878447430a4","tid":1911823,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4417ac581aa5aa769ea8e5a73d81cba8c009fd0e","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"121610ddc308ee5f80e2584804735ba97ff99ec9","tid":1911823,"uid":141097,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2a3d7168d5cb5bc9a8223e6832d23e81486b33c0","tid":1911823,"uid":27553,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"熱狗屌自己人仲落力過建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:21:03.000Z","msg":"屌敵人嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:24:08.000Z","msg":"不斷笑鳩同路人最有用<br />\n一副眾人皆醉唯我獨醒既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:47:15.000Z","msg":"泛民做錯又唔屌得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8b01f35bc2e929c7d99658c4bd5cde5c819f09","tid":1911823,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0